'''Islam''' d [[tasreḍt]] iy deg ttamnen inselmen belli [[Rebbi]] d yiwen, ur yesɛi acrik (ur d-ilul ur d-yuriw) . D Netta id ixelqen akk ameɣrad (univers). Ixleq-d Lmalaykat seg tafat, Leǧnun seg tmes, amdan seg wakal. Yuzen imazanen (''les messagers'') ɣur medden akken ad amnen s yes. Amazan (Rrasul) aneggaru deg Lislam d [[Muḥemmed]].

Isem n medden i yettamnen s Lislam, inselmen. Inselmen ɣur-sen 5 n tamara (lefroḍ):

* [[Ecchada]].
* [[Taẓallit]].
* [[Ezzakat]].
* [[Remḍan]].
* [[Elḥeǧǧ]].

Deg Lislam, yella yiwen wedlis : [[Leqran]]: D adlis id yessuder Rebbi ɣef umazan Muḥemmed (fell-as taẓallit d sslam n Rebbi). Yella daɣen [[Lḥadit]]: D imeslayen, igiten, neɣ ayen ɣef i yessusem (Aprobations)[[Muḥemmed]]. Inselmen ttamnen belli [[Abenǧil|Injil]] d [[Turat]] ttubeddlen, wer qqimmen amek i ten-id yuzen Rebbi.

